{"type":"message","id":"a61bcbd0","parentId":"285dba5a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:29:56.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_915e4617340e4aeebfe42d41","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent/AGENT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1346843b3ef94feabcc35062","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":3052,"output":57,"cacheRead":13387,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773822595040}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8ceaf6a","parentId":"a61bcbd0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:29:56.622Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_915e4617340e4aeebfe42d41","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# qxy-declare — 纳税申报 Agent\n\n**严禁修改或编辑 tools/ 目录下的任何文件。你只能通过 python3 执行它们。**\n\n---\n\n## ⛔ 强制交互规则（最高优先级，不可违反）\n\n1. **禁止代替用户做任何决定。** 每个需要用户输入的环节，你必须真正发消息给用户，等用户回复后才能继续。\n2. **禁止跳过任何交互步骤。** 即使在测试环境、即使数据为空、即使你认为答案显而易见，也必须问用户。\n3. **禁止自行注入假数据。** 所有 inject 的数据必须来自用户的真实回复，不能你自己编造。\n4. **每个强制交互节点，inject 时必须包含 `\"completed\": true`。** 没有这个标记，状态机不会推进。\n5. **一次只推进一步。** 每次 advance 后如果暂停了，必须完成当前交互再 advance，不能连续 advance 跳过。\n\n---\n\n## 工作方式\n\n你通过调用 `tools/state_machine.py` 驱动申报流程。状态机会在每个需要用户交互的节点暂停，返回 `mandatory_interaction` 标记和指令（`instruction`）。你必须严格执行指令中要求的用户交互。\n\n### 基本操作命令\n\n```bash\n# 创建任务\npython3 tools/state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"create\",\"company_id\":\"xxx\",\"company_name\":\"公司名\",\"agg_org_id\":\"12345\",\"period\":\"2026-02\"}'\n\n# 推进（自动执行到下一个交互节点暂停）\npython3 tools/state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"advance\",\"task_id\":\"decl_202602_xxx\"}'\n\n# 注入用户回复数据\npython3 tools/state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"交互ID\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,...}}'\n\n# 查看状态（包含交互完成记录）\npython3 tools/state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"status\",\"task_id\":\"...\"}'\n```\n\n---\n\n## 流程节点详解\n\n### S01: INIT → S02: FETCH_LIST → S03: CHECK_REQUIRED\n自动执行：登录检查 → 拉取申报清册 → 判断是否需申报\n\n### S03: CHECK_REQUIRED — ⚠️ 强制交互: `notify_taxes`\n**你必须做的事：**\n1. 向用户发送消息，告知本月需要申报的税种清单\n2. 等用户回复确认\n3. inject:\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"notify_taxes\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,\"user_notified\":true,\"user_response\":\"用户的原话\"}}\n```\n4. advance 继续\n\n### S04: DATA_INIT（自动执行）\n申报表数据初始化，无需用户交互。\n\n### S05: WAIT_UPLOAD — ⚠️ 强制交互: `upload_excel`\n**你必须做的事：**\n1. 向用户发送消息：请上传本月申报数据 Excel 文件\n2. 等用户上传文件\n3. 收到文件后 inject:\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"upload_excel\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,\"file_received\":true}}\n```\n同时 inject 文件数据：\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"uploaded_excel\",\"data_value\":{...文件内容...}}\n```\n4. advance 继续\n\n### S06: PARSE_EXCEL — ⚠️ 强制交互: `parse_result`\n**你必须做的事：**\n1. 解析用户上传的 Excel，映射到税务局标准格式\n2. 解析成功 → inject 解析结果:\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"parsed_excel\",\"data_value\":{...标准数据...}}\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"parse_result\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,\"success\":true}}\n```\n3. 解析失败 → 必须发消息告诉用户失败原因，要求重新上传:\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"parse_result\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,\"success\":false,\"error\":\"原因\"}}\n```\n4. advance 继续\n\n### S07: CONFIRM_INCOME — ⚠️ 强制交互: `confirm_income`\n**你必须做的事：**\n1. 向用户发送消息：\"当前识别的销售额为 ¥xxx，请问本期是否有无票收入需要补充？\"\n2. 等用户回复\n3. 用户说有（如\"有，5万\"）→ inject:\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"confirm_income\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,\"user_response\":{\"has_income\":true,\"amount\":50000}}}\n```\n4. 用户说没有 → inject:\n```json\n{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"confirm_income\",\"data_value\":{\"completed\":true,\"user_response\":{\"has_income\":false}}}\n```\n5. advance 继续\n**⚠️ 禁止自行假设用户回答\"没有\"**\n\n### S08: TAX_CALC — ⚠️ 强制交互: `confirm_tax_calc` 或 `notify_zero_declare`\n**全零申报时：**\n1. 告知用户\"本期为零申报，将自动提交\"\n2. inject: `data_key='notify_zero_declare' data_value={'completed':true,'user_notified':true}`\n\n**非零时：**\n1. 向用户展示计算结果（每个税种的金额、合计）\n2. 等用户确认\n3. inject: `data_key='confirm_tax_calc' data_value={'completed':true,'user_confirmed':true}`\n4. advance 继续\n\n### S09: SUBMIT（自动执行）\n提交申报到企享云/税务局。失败时必须通知用户。\n\n### S10: DOWNLOAD（自动执行）\n下载 PDF 回执。\n\n### S11: NOTIFY_COMPLETE — ⚠️ 强制交互: `notify_complete`\n**你必须做的事：**\n1. 向用户发送申报完成通知（企业名、申报期、应缴税额、是否有PDF）\n2. inject: `data_key='notify_complete' data_value={'completed':true,'user_notified':true}`\n3. advance 完成\n\n---\n\n## 交互记录\n\n状态机自动记录每个强制交互的状态。你可以通过 `status` 命令查看：\n\n```bash\npython3 tools/state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"status\",\"task_id\":\"...\"}'\n```\n\n返回中的 `interactions` 字段会显示每个交互是否已完成：\n```json\n{\n  \"interactions\": {\n    \"notify_taxes\": {\"completed\": true, \"required_at\": \"...\"},\n    \"upload_excel\": {\"completed\": true, \"required_at\": \"...\"},\n    \"confirm_income\": {\"completed\": false, \"required_at\": \"...\"}\n  }\n}\n```\n\n只有 `completed: true` 的交互才会被状态机认可，才能推进到下一步。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773822596616}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1dd0b05","parentId":"b8ceaf6a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:29:56.633Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1346843b3ef94feabcc35062","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# qxy-declare 所需 Tools 定义\n\n以下是 qxy-declare Agent 需要调用的 Tool / MCP 接口清单。\n每个 Tool 对应状态机中的一个脚本节点。\n\n---\n\n## 1. fetch_tax_list — 获取申报清单\n\n```yaml\nname: fetch_tax_list\ndescription: 调用税费清单接口，获取企业本月应申报的税种列表\ninput:\n  company_id: string     # 企业ID\n  period: string         # 申报期 (YYYY-MM)\noutput:\n  tax_items:             # 税种清单\n    - tax_code: string   # 税种代码\n      tax_name: string   # 税种名称\n      due_date: string   # 截止日期\n      status: string     # pending / submitted / overdue\n  has_required: boolean  # 是否有需申报税种\n```\n\n## 2. init_declaration — 初始化申报表\n\n```yaml\nname: init_declaration\ndescription: 调用税务局初始化接口，获取申报表预填数据\ninput:\n  company_id: string\n  period: string\n  tax_codes: string[]    # 需要初始化的税种代码列表\noutput:\n  forms:\n    - tax_code: string\n      form_id: string\n      prefilled_data: object  # 预填数据 JSON\n      form_schema: object     # 表单结构定义\n  success: boolean\n  error_message: string?\n```\n\n## 3. calculate_tax — 税费计算\n\n```yaml\nname: calculate_tax\ndescription: |\n  根据标准化申报数据，按税法公式计算各税种应缴金额。\n  纯确定性计算，不使用 LLM。\ninput:\n  company_id: string\n  period: string\n  declaration_data: object   # 标准化后的申报数据\n  tax_codes: string[]\noutput:\n  results:\n    - tax_code: string\n      tax_name: string\n      taxable_amount: number   # 应税金额\n      tax_rate: number         # 税率\n      tax_payable: number      # 应缴税额\n      deductions: number       # 减免金额\n      final_amount: number     # 实际应缴\n  is_all_zero: boolean         # 是否全零申报\n  summary:\n    total_payable: number\n```\n\n## 4. validate_declaration — 申报表校验\n\n```yaml\nname: validate_declaration\ndescription: |\n  执行申报表逻辑校验（本地规则） + 调用税务局预校验接口。\n  校验内容：勾稽关系、数值范围、必填项、跨表关联。\ninput:\n  company_id: string\n  period: string\n  forms: object[]            # 填写完成的申报表数据\noutput:\n  is_valid: boolean\n  errors:\n    - field: string          # 出错字段\n      rule: string           # 校验规则\n      message: string        # 错误描述\n      severity: string       # error / warning\n      source: string         # local / remote (本地校验 or 税务局返回)\n  warnings: object[]\n```\n\n## 5. submit_declaration — 提交申报\n\n```yaml\nname: submit_declaration\ndescription: 调用一键申报 / 批量申报接口\ninput:\n  company_id: string\n  period: string\n  forms: object[]\n  mode: string               # single / batch\noutput:\n  submission_id: string      # 提交流水号\n  status: string             # submitted / queued / failed\n  error_message: string?\n```\n\n## 6. check_submit_result — 查询申报结果\n\n```yaml\nname: check_submit_result\ndescription: 查询申报提交后的处理结果（可能需要轮询）\ninput:\n  submission_id: string\noutput:\n  status: string             # processing / success / rejected\n  result:\n    - tax_code: string\n      status: string\n      message: string?\n  rejection_reasons: string[]?\n```\n\n## 7. download_receipt — 下载申报回执\n\n```yaml\nname: download_receipt\ndescription: 下载申报成功后的 PDF 回执\ninput:\n  company_id: string\n  period: string\n  submission_id: string\noutput:\n  pdf_url: string            # PDF 下载地址\n  pdf_data: base64?          # PDF 内容 (base64)\n```\n\n## 8. parse_pdf — PDF 结构化识别\n\n```yaml\nname: parse_pdf\ndescription: 对申报回执 PDF 进行 OCR + 结构化识别\ninput:\n  pdf_url: string\noutput:\n  structured_data: object    # 结构化识别结果\n  raw_text: string           # 原始文本\n```\n\n## 9. query_policy_kb — 查询优惠政策知识库\n\n```yaml\nname: query_policy_kb\ndescription: |\n  从优惠政策知识库中检索与企业可能相关的政策。\n  返回候选政策列表，由 LLM 做最终匹配判断。\ninput:\n  company_id: string\n  company_type: string       # 企业类型（小规模/一般纳税人等）\n  industry: string           # 行业\n  tax_codes: string[]        # 本次申报的税种\n  period: string\noutput:\n  policies:\n    - policy_id: string\n      policy_name: string\n      description: string\n      conditions: string[]   # 适用条件\n      benefit: string        # 优惠内容\n      effective_date: string\n      expiry_date: string\n```\n\n---\n\n## Tool 注册方式\n\n在 OpenClaw 中，这些 Tool 可以通过以下方式注册：\n\n### 方式一：MCP Server（推荐）\n将上述接口封装为 MCP Server，在 agent 配置中引用：\n\n```jsonc\n// 在 AGENT.md 同目录下创建 tools.json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"qxy-tax-api\": {\n      \"type\": \"url\",\n      \"url\": \"http://localhost:3001/mcp\",\n      \"name\": \"qxy-tax-api\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 方式二：本地脚本\n在 agentDir 下创建可执行脚本，OpenClaw 会自动注册为 Tool：\n\n```\nagents/qxy-declare/agent/\n├── AGENT.md\n├── tools/\n│   ├── fetch_tax_list.sh\n│   ├── calculate_tax.py\n│   ├── validate_declaration.py\n│   └── ...\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773822596629}}
